attributes.background:
MPs salary should be set at 2x the national average, as defined by ONS;
Additional Housing Allowances should be scrapped;
Travel costs should be re-imbursed at cost, and against receipts;
Reasonable staff provision (1 x researcher, 1 x PA) should be provided centrally, and recruited through fair and open competition;
MPs should be barred from holding other paid employment whilst serving as an MP;
